    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "people don't understand though. they say \"it gets better\" or \"just keep trying\" but it's just more of the same. it's like being a different species. even when i'm around people i feel completely alone. it just feels so heavy. like the effort of existing is way more than the reward i'm getting from it. does it ever actually stop feeling like this?",
